Module gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind
Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations

Annotation Type XmlNs

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(ANNOTATION_TYPE) public @interface XmlNs
Used to identify the XML namespace to use for a set of annotated Java classes.

  • Required Element Summary

    Required Elements
    Modifier and Type
    Required Element
    Description

    namespace
    Defines the Namespace URI for this namespace.

    Optional Element

  • Element Details

    • namespace

      String namespace
      Defines the Namespace URI for this namespace.
      Returns:
      the associated namespace

    • prefix

      String prefix
      Suggests a namespace prefix to use for generated code.

      If the value is "##none", then there is no prefix defined.

      Returns:
      the associated namespace prefix
      Default:
      "##none"
